'''Gradska Plaža Stadium''' ({{lang-mk|Cтадион „Градска Плажа“}}) is a [[multi-purpose stadium]] in [[Struga]], [[Republic of Macedonia]]. It has a capacity of about 500<ref>http://www.macedonianfootball.com/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=114:karaorman&catid=27:3-liga-jugozapad-third-league-south-west&Itemid=122</ref> and it is currently the home ground of [[FK Karaorman]] and [[FC Struga]].

